{"id":"278799081_Equivalence_classes_of_permutations_modulo_descents_and_left-to-right_maxima","abstract":"In a recent paper [2], the authors provide enumerating results for equivalence classes of permutations modulo excedances. In this paper we investigate two other equivalence relations based on descents and left-to-right maxima. Enumerating results are presented for permutations, involutions, derangements, cycles and permutations avoiding one pattern of length three.","authors":["Armen Petrossiana","Jean-Luc Baril"],"meta":["June 2014Pure Mathematics and Applications 25(1)","DOI:10.1515/puma-2015-0002"],"references":["280445715_The_On-Line_Encyclopedia_of_Integer_Sequences","273442926_Equivalence_classes_of_permutations_modulo_excedances","319394668_The_On-Line_Encyclopedia_of_Integer_Sequences","279837792_Permutations_with_forbidden_subsequences_and_stack-sortable_permutations","275985594_Enumerative_Combinatorics_Volume_1","274207339_The_Art_of_Computer_Programming--Errata_et_Addenda","268992235_Patterns_in_Permutations_and_Words","265445639_Restricted_Permutations","265369152_Theorie_Geometrique_des_Polynomes_Euleriens","262493823_The_Art_of_Computer_Programming","256720566_Statistics-preserving_bijections_between_classical_and_cyclic_permutations","262155109_Satisfiability_and_The_Art_of_Computer_Programming","246076812_Enumerative_combinatorics_Vol_I","239595553_Combinatorics_of_compositions_and_words_Discrete_Mathematics_and_its_Applications_Boca_Raton","230801367_Restricted_132-Avoiding_Permutations"]}